    "description": "Mech Wars 是一款多人在线游戏，进行实时的 6 对 6 团队战斗！<br>通过摧毁、占领和升级你的机械战士来赢得胜利，成为 Mech 机器人在线世界中最强大的指挥官。在玩机械战斗游戏时，展示你的力量和技能对于赢得战斗至关重要。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/ab9946c1294204c3103ea5ef653b76d9.poster.avif?t=1726041990\" width=624 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/ab9946c1294204c3103ea5ef653b76d9.webm?t=1726041990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/ab9946c1294204c3103ea5ef653b76d9.mp4?t=1726041990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>创建你的机器人军队，使用适合你游戏风格的武器组合，并加入战斗。占领敌人的基地或摧毁所有对手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/8b9eab2f667ef8d1a9db83baadefa1a2.poster.avif?t=1726041990\" width=624 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/8b9eab2f667ef8d1a9db83baadefa1a2.webm?t=1726041990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/8b9eab2f667ef8d1a9db83baadefa1a2.mp4?t=1726041990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>组建你自己的机器人团队，装备特殊武器，在激烈的 6 对 6 战斗中获胜。进入战场，与其他战争机器展开高风险的战斗，争夺霸主地位！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/8aaa589f7a9036346c95cdb38f875199.poster.avif?t=1726041990\" width=624 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/8aaa589f7a9036346c95cdb38f875199.webm?t=1726041990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>使用各种战术，如跳跃到建筑物上、躲在盾牌后面或将机器人传送到敌人的防线后方，以你喜欢的风格进行游戏。在进步的同时，你还会通过提升等级获得每日奖励。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/0be59da684c7da2ae9fa86d7b7534d0c.poster.avif?t=1726041990\" width=624 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/0be59da684c7da2ae9fa86d7b7534d0c.webm?t=1726041990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037010/extras/0be59da684c7da2ae9fa86d7b7534d0c.mp4?t=1726041990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>准备好在游戏中体验激烈的机器人行动，其中包括攻击模式和死亡竞赛模式！在攻击模式中，玩家需要作为一个团队合作完成目标并击败敌人。在死亡竞赛模式中，每个机器人为自己而战，玩家们在战场上争夺主导地位。<br><br>加入 Mech Wars 的宇宙，体验摧毁敌人和收集珍贵的机械碎片的胜利快感。每次胜利后，你都会获得免费的奖励，帮助你成为终极机械指挥官！",
